{"tid":2153734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Solomon Yue：正式澄清, 我係反對強迫香港人不交稅, 反對強迫香港人進行「自殺式任務」","createTime":"2020-08-12T17:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T05:06:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":114,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf16e2a0a66e59660cbf6619fed3f6a2a1b3c7c","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"有連登仔扭曲Solomon Yue的說話, 而家Solomon Yue要正式澄清.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共和黨Solomon Yue:<br />\n- 我反對強迫任何香港人進行「自殺式任務」 .<br />\n- 我反對反對強迫香港人&quot;不交稅&quot;, 因為&quot;不交稅&quot;正正係「自殺式任務」 .<br />\n- 香港抗爭者應該參考(印度)甘地的抗爭手法, 而不應該仿傚巴勒斯坦式抗爭 (<em>不斷推人去死</em>).<br />\n- 有人若鼓吹&quot;推人去死&quot;, 香港手足應該反對.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1293588731484487680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1293588731484487680&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7f3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=7774632f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1293588731484487680&h=1e49789c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1293588731484487680</a>"},{"pid":"bf8ca75aed79e4e09448b9677ca7893acf2c2d8a","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦如何推人去死:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://zh-hans.danielpipes.org/article/5874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh-hans.danielpipes.org%2Farticle%2F5874&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7f3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=badcf67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://zh-hans.danielpipes.org/article/5874</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>巴勒斯坦政權（以下簡稱ＰＡ）鼓動易受感動的年輕人，鼓吹殺死以色列人的自殺行動是榮耀的。<br />\n....<br />\n  總之，哈德遜研究所的小學生教育方面的專家Meyrav Wurmser說， PA已經發展了&ldquo;一套國家經營的意識形態，就是強迫［兒童］去送死&rdquo;。為什麼這種灌輸會奏效，為什麼巴勒斯坦的家長熱情的送他們的孩子去死？什麼樣的壓力可以戰勝人類保護自己所愛的孩子的本能呢？</em>"},{"pid":"bacf0e2e11cd5ef84c52c8e7204e04da39655ba5","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"另外....<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦支持中國立港區國安法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2091965/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2091965/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"37ea8ba3a76fb177297bc30d1217cedd76b27431","tid":2153734,"uid":143343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"801c06ad9d074284eba4c2544f224a7d2b2723df","tid":2153734,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"同恐怖份子政權有金錢來往<br />\n國際可否制裁埋我"},{"pid":"8bb81ad218672011c065f5867a1055a26dd3e9de","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"37ea8ba3a76fb177297bc30d1217cedd76b27431","tid":2153734,"uid":143343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"佢下次真係要小心D翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5873aff494922212c5910077eb5f4c5795b4d1ef","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"801c06ad9d074284eba4c2544f224a7d2b2723df","tid":2153734,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"同恐怖份子政權有金錢來往<br />\n國際可否制裁埋我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"Solomon Yue講到咁, 美國應該唔會怪責香港人被迫交稅."},{"pid":"8078f9753800ded05ce57650301815611799ffb3","tid":2153734,"uid":276887,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"推呢個, 出面太多標題黨"},{"pid":"77b485e30e1fab9230329a3a594691f79fe175c6","tid":2153734,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8078f9753800ded05ce57650301815611799ffb3","tid":2153734,"uid":276887,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"推呢個, 出面太多標題黨"}